A vintage-style illustration of a cozy Singapore shopping scene at night: a woman with dark hair sits at a retail counter, examining three different mobile phones laid out before her like precious objects, while a helpful shop assistant gestures warmly toward the devices. The scene is bathed in warm amber light from retro hanging lamps, with display cases full of early 2000s flip phones and candy bar phones glowing softly in the background. The color palette features rich teals, warm oranges, and cream tones reminiscent of 1960s travel posters. Through the shop window, the Singapore night skyline twinkles. The mood is intimate and surprisingly pleasant, capturing a rare moment of genuine customer care in a consumer electronics setting.
